    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 10th level, you add the @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.04nMsTWkIFvkbXlY]{Polymorph} spell to your spellbook, if it is not there already. You can cast @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.04nMsTWkIFvkbXlY]{Polymorph} without expending a spell slot. When you do so, you can target only yourself and transform into a beast whose challenge rating is 1 or lower.</p>\n<p>Once you cast @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.04nMsTWkIFvkbXlY]{Polymorph} in this way, you can't do so again until you finish a short or long rest, though you can still cast it normally using an available spell slot.</p>",
